125
00:23:14,030 --> 00:23:20,250
First, Hong Kong has been lucky to have built up such a reputation as an international financial centre.

126
00:23:20,980 --> 00:23:25,360
This is mainly attributable to a good environment of doing business.

127
00:23:25,640 --> 00:23:28,480
which I can say is one of the best in the world.

128
00:23:29,520 --> 00:23:35,840
一數個核心價值是 indispensablе in maintaining such a favourable business environment.

