00:23:36,560 --> 00:23:42,280
這些核心價值包括我們的法治，自由資訊的自由流通。

130
00:23:42,710 --> 00:23:45,350
一relatively corruption-free society.

131
00:23:45,900 --> 00:23:49,920
一個fair and transparent regulatory regulatory regime.

132
00:23:50,990 --> 00:23:56,190
Now of course, as I today, I must say this with a pinch of salt.

133
00:23:56,530 --> 00:24:01,660
especially when we are saying that Hong Kong is relatively corruption free because

134
00:24:01,960 --> 00:24:04,440
As you have noted, Mr. President.

135
00:24:04,720 --> 00:24:08,760
