146
00:24:53,320 --> 00:24:54,630
On the one hand.

147
00:24:54,970 --> 00:24:59,650
We want it to be fair and flexible in order to stimulate innovation.

148
00:25:00,280 --> 00:25:05,930
On the other hand, we would want to give adequate protection to consumers and investors.

149
00:25:07,870 --> 00:25:11,620
