155
00:25:38,260 --> 00:25:48,060
now this attitude is quite harmful because it often gives rise to deep-rooted disagreement between stakeholders, mainly the market players and the government.

156
00:25:48,340 --> 00:25:58,010
Even during the very first consultation stage of any regulatory proposal, now the recent examples I can tell you, Mr. President.

157
00:25:58,290 --> 00:26:04,450
