160
00:26:26,120 --> 00:26:27,930
公司 insolventcy regime。

161
00:26:28,210 --> 00:26:29,990
and also, of course.

162
00:26:30,270 --> 00:26:36,380
My honourable friend, Sinchungkai, spoke about the regulatory of investment-linked insurance products.

163
00:26:37,160 --> 00:26:47,840
